@Tetyanka It seems that you are using the WebDriver provided by PHPUnit. It is different from this project now because we are rewriting everything.

In your script, 

```
$driver->session->open('http://www.google.com');
```

we no longer have `WebDriver::session` anymore.

1) click the button

```
$SaveButton->click();
```

2a) using WebDriverExpectedCondition

```
$this->driver->wait()->until(
  WebDriverExpectedCondition::visibilityOfElementLocated(
    WebDriverBy::XXXXX(YYYYY) // locate the $Loader
  )
);
```

2b) using closure if the pre-written expected condition does not fit

```
$this->driver->wait()->until(function ($driver) use ($Loader) {
  // return a truthy(eg true, an object) to stop waiting, return a falsy(eg false, null) to retry 
  return $Loader->isDisplayed();
});
```

You might need to find the `$Loader` inside the closure if the $Loader is redrawn.

```
